        "username": "Philip_Ente",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/philip_ente/{size}/964_2.png",
        "created_at": "2018-01-04T15:46:53.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"William Kelley\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n William Kelley:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>He also uses great corks.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>good pickup</p>\n<p>Benoit goes to Spain every year to personally select  his corks from a boutique producer.  I have seen other winemakers in Burgundy admire his corks and ask him where they came from, but he will not tell, due to the extremely limited production.</p>",
