        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/t/5e9695/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2018-01-05T00:28:34.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Happened upon this thread this morning and saw the 2015 Benoit Ente Bourgogne Golden Jubilee on a list at lunch. Tried it. It\u2019s fantastic. Pure. High acidity. Just my style. So thanks for this thread! I love the Arnaud Ente stuff for that purity and acidity \u2026 nice to find this at a bit lower price.</p>",
